tweet: The UK banned barren battery cages for egg-laying hens back in 2012 - yet the UK Government may now allow the import of eggs from hens in these systems, undermining our standards and British farmers' livelihoods. Sign our petition to stop this:  https://t.co/7nQlmb0AB3 #AgriBill  https://t.co/dDDg7GPn71
name: RSPCA (England & Wales)
